---
description: To run Slang tests
globs: 
---

- Use "slang-test.exe", which will be present in "build.vs2022/Debug/bin/" after Slang is built. 
- To run all Slang tests (takes a long time), no need to give any arguments
- To run a specific test use "tests/<folder>/<test-name>" as the argument (without the .slang extension)

